# The repository-root .gitignore ignores everything ('*') and then whitelists
# only a few source extensions (*.cpp, *.h, *.png, *.svg, *.txt, *.sh).
# That silently drops this project's audio, fonts and docs. Re-include them
# here so a fresh clone actually has the assets the game loads.

!.gitignore
!*.md
!*.wav
!*.ttf
!*.py

# Build artifacts (chess, chess-cli) and object files have no whitelisted
# extension, so the root '*' already ignores them. Runtime save state:
Save.txt
